Package org.jruyi.me

JRuyi Messaging Engine Package Version 1.0

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IConsumer
    A consumer consumes messages routed to it via the message queue.
    IEndpoint
    An entity produces/consumes messages.
    IMessage
    A message is a data carrier to be routed in the message queue.
    IPostHandler
    Service for handling messages going into the message queue.
    IPreHandler
    Service for handling messages leaving the message queue.
    IProcessor
    Service for processing messages.
    IProducer
    A producer is used to create messages able to be put into the message queue for routing.
    IRoute
    A route defines a rule for messages to be routed between two end points in one way.
    IRouteSet
    A IRouteSet consists of and administers all the IRoutes having the same from.
    IRoutingTable
    A collection of IRouteSets.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MeConstants
    Defines standard names for Message Engine's constants.
